Package org.ensor.algorithms.toposort

This package contains a generic topological sort algorithm.

See: Description

Package org.ensor.algorithms.toposort Description

This package contains a generic topological sort algorithm. The algorithm can be used any time a dependency tree needs to be resolved so that tasks or nodes of the tree can be traversed in such a way as to enforce the graph established. Examples include module initialization order and order of tasks to be performed by a robot where the ordering of the steps is important.
